$NetBSD: patch-scripts_zm_in,v 1.3 2015/04/05 08:51:08 dsainty Exp $

/etc/rc.d/init.d/functions doesn't commonly exist.

The LOCKFILE feature appears unused, and requires a /var/lock/subsys directory
we don't have.

